==English==

===Noun===
'''hypothesis''' ({{plural}} [[hypotheses]])

#A [[tentative]] [[conjecture]] [[explaining]] an [[observation]], [[phenomenon]], or [[scientific]] [[problem]] that can be [[test]]ed by [[further]] [[investigation]]
#an [[assumption]] taken to be [[true]] for the [[purpose]] of [[argument]] or [[investigation]]
# {{grammar}} the [[antecedent]] of a [[conditional]] [[statement]] 

